{"tid":2209054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇識過一啲冇講粗口嘅朋友?","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T17:59:43.000Z","uid":124893,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a08f6b504bcfef5195d8ba47eb5469dd5671c7f9","tid":2209054,"uid":124893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"自己識過一位咁樣嘅人，其餘都係以粗口作為句子構成主要部分嘅朋友或者同學。<br />\n<br />\n雖然個位朋友唔係話好成績突出同靚仔，但有種感覺係一個好脾氣同易相處嘅人，我都好想試吓個種唔講粗口嘅氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無奈有時同朋友溝通少咗啲助語詞好似唔係好慣。<br />\n<br />\n真心羨慕啲唔講粗口嘅人，因為講過之後變咗會一舖癮咁戒唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2087e8948363a741e52ed7e937c3916adce931a8","tid":2209054,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:10:02.000Z","msg":"心癮，又會想偷偷出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f076c1883941b3696fc5f425aaf0066d988627d","tid":2209054,"uid":310266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"對住老母從來唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40430c8c1600d47a5cd3803977d36684e4a0135","tid":2209054,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"我自己從來都唔講"},{"pid":"6fc5ce1cd35a735d514ecc4f4b94198591e3034e","tid":2209054,"uid":340004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"從來唔講粗口，一有不滿就直接開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3546b9887fa3680dd12ca26dde977f2e835d181b","tid":2209054,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"喂屌~你~老~母食左飯未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05173739d5769477c6e6adc8cf1178e1542742bf","tid":2209054,"uid":368147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"講粗口有親切感啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c29539a06cb73662b58eb7661f931701783057","tid":2209054,"uid":124893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"屋企人講得最多，但係冇喺屋企講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ac8487f8f9a4b4fa5ab87f2139402bd9c9c3a1","tid":2209054,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"1a7a06e3538f45d7d0783ceb7ae2d2b694d1a7b5","tid":2209054,"uid":296664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人喺連登都唔講"}]}